            description "for marking"
            ingress
                default-action fc be profile in
                dscp be fc be profile in
                dscp cs1 fc l2 profile in
                dscp cs2 fc l2 profile in
                dscp cs3 fc l2 profile in
                dscp cs4 fc h1 profile in
                dscp cs5 fc af profile in
                dscp nc1 fc nc profile in
                dscp nc2 fc af profile in
                lsp-exp 0 fc be profile in
                lsp-exp 1 fc l2 profile in
                lsp-exp 2 fc l2 profile in
                lsp-exp 3 fc l1 profile in
                lsp-exp 4 fc h1 profile in
                lsp-exp 5 fc af profile in
                lsp-exp 6 fc nc profile in
                lsp-exp 7 fc af profile in
                dot1p 1 fc af profile out
                dot1p 3 fc l2 profile out
                dot1p 5 fc nc profile out
                dot1p 7 fc af profile out
            exit
            egress
                remarking
                fc af
                    dscp-in-profile cs5
                    dscp-out-profile cs5
                    lsp-exp-in-profile 5
                    lsp-exp-out-profile 5
                exit
                fc h1
                    dscp-in-profile cs4
                    dscp-out-profile cs4
                    lsp-exp-in-profile 4
                    lsp-exp-out-profile 4
                exit
                fc l1
                    lsp-exp-out-profile 3
                exit
                fc l2
                    lsp-exp-in-profile 3
                    lsp-exp-out-profile 3
                exit
                fc nc
                    dscp-in-profile nc1
                    dscp-out-profile nc1
                    lsp-exp-in-profile 6
                    lsp-exp-out-profile 6
                exit
            exit
        exit
    exit

echo "BGP Configuration"
#--------------------------------------------------
        bgp
            family ipv4 vpn-ipv4
            multipath 8
            ibgp-multipath
            local-as 64759
            router-id 61.130.159.24
            next-hop-resolution
                use-bgp-routes
            exit
            group "ibgp"
                family vpn-ipv4
                type internal
                peer-as 64759
                local-address 61.130.159.24
                neighbor 61.174.80.20
                    description "JH-JH-CN-RR-C7304-2.MAN"
                exit
                neighbor 61.174.80.21
                    description "JH-JH-CZ-RR-C7304-2.MAN"
                exit

                exit
                neighbor 61.174.80.90
                    description "JH-JH-CZ-RR-C7304-1.MAN"
                exit
            exit
            group "pgCR"
                family ipv4
                keepalive 60
                hold-time 180
                type internal
                preference 200
                export "rpSET_COMM_OUT" 
                local-as 64759
                peer-as 64759
                local-address 61.130.159.24
                neighbor 61.130.158.4
                    description "to:JH-JH-CZ-CR-1.MAN.CRS"
                exit
                neighbor 61.130.158.8
                    description "to:JH-JH-CZ-CR-1.MAN.CRS"
                exit
            exit
            no shutdown
        exit

            shutdown

                far-end 61.130.159.16 ing-svc-label 5555
            exit 
        exit 
        mirror-dest 1001 create
            shutdown
            remote-source
                far-end 61.130.159.16 ing-svc-label 4444
            exit 
        exit 
    exit
